cs.LO, cs.CC, cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.FL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with first order logic and its extension with modulo counting quantifiers. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely as the paper discusses circuit complexity classes and the separation of ACC0 and NC1. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) are possible categories as the paper involves mathematical concepts such as regular languages and positional normal form. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the definability of regular languages in a logic.
